  "description": "<h4>Application</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Lexus IS200/IS300 1st Gen GXE10/JCE10/SXE10 1999-2005</li>\n<li>Toyota Altezza XE10 1998-2005</li>\n<li>Toyota Mark II 9th Gen JZX110 2000-2007</li>\n<li>Toyota Verossa X110 2001-2004</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Package Includes</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Front coilovers × 2 pcs</li>\n<li>Rear coilovers × 2 pcs</li>\n<li>Wrench × 2 pcs</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Features</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Mono-tube shock design provides larger capacity of oil and gas</li>\n<li>Adjustable ride height</li>\n<li>Adjustable pre-load spring tension</li>\n<li>Hi-Tensile performance spring - Under 600,000 times continuous testing with less than 0.04% spring distortion</li>\n<li>Special surface treatment improves durability and performance</li>\n<li>Includes fitted rubber boots to protect dampers and maintain cleanliness</li>\n<li>Improved handling performance without sacrificing ride comfort</li>\n<li>Fast and affordable appearance upgrade</li>\n<li>Easy installation with proper tools</li>\n<li>Ideal for track, drift, fast road and daily driving</li>\n<li>All accessories shown in photos included</li>\n<li>Default 1-year warranty for any manufacturing defect, upgrade to 2 years with our Extended Warranty Program</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Technical Specifications</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Spring rate Front: 12 kg/mm</li>\n<li>Spring rate Rear: 10 kg/mm</li>\n<li>Adjustable height: Yes</li>\n<li>Adjustable camber plate: No</li>\n<li>Adjustable damper: Non-adjustable</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Warranty</h4>\n<p>All items include a standard 1-year warranty from date of purchase. Proof of purchase (order number preferred) is required. For faster warranty claims, please provide images/videos of the issue. Returning defective items is typically not necessary. Additional information may be requested to properly diagnose and resolve issues.</p>",
